{
  "texts": [
    "Technology has added many new elements to the world of education.",
    "The term \"digital generation\" applies to children born in this period, who are immersed by technology in their immediate environment.",
    "In this regard, the National Council of Teachers of Mathematics (2014) recommends adopting and integrating new technology in the classroom to improve the bar for mathematics instruction and advance equity.",
    "ChatGPT is starting to show promise as a teaching and learning method for mathematics (Baidoo-Anu & Ansah, 2023).",
    "It can be seen that there is an increasing trend towards AI in mathematics education research (Hwang et al., 2023)."
  ]
}